16:11.839 --> 16:14.239
Can I crash
at your place?

16:14.241 --> 16:16.509
No, I sold my place.
I'm back at Smurf's.

16:16.511 --> 16:17.776
Oh, perfect.

16:17.778 --> 16:19.512
More room,
and I can...
No.

16:19.514 --> 16:20.980
...start
swimming laps again.

16:20.982 --> 16:23.516
No. No.
You can crash here.

16:23.518 --> 16:26.385
I got a couch
in the office.

16:26.387 --> 16:28.654
That couch sucks.

16:28.656 --> 16:30.523
Really gonna
roll out the red carpet

16:30.525 --> 16:33.159
for your old man,
huh?

16:34.729 --> 16:36.662
Listen.
[ Clears throat ]

16:36.664 --> 16:39.665
What do you need
this shit for?

16:39.667 --> 16:42.201
That's not
