16:42.203 --> 16:43.802
The guys who are dishing it out
are gonna want to know

16:43.804 --> 16:46.205
they ain't gonna be left
holding the bag.

16:46.207 --> 16:52.144
♪♪

16:52.146 --> 16:54.013
Pope got locked up.

16:54.015 --> 16:56.415
