listen to me, okay?

17:08.763 --> 17:10.696
Number one,
Pope getting locked up

17:10.698 --> 17:12.097
is a
positive development

17:12.099 --> 17:16.435
for all of
civilized society, okay?

17:16.437 --> 17:17.836
Number two --

17:17.838 --> 17:21.707
man, you're talking about
US Marshalls now.

17:21.709 --> 17:24.843
You're gonna have to
leave the country.

17:24.845 --> 17:27.713
And you won't be able
to come back.

17:27.715 --> 17:29.582
Ever.

17:29.584 --> 17:32.985
♪♪

17:38.125 --> 17:40.926
These are good.

17:40.928 --> 17:43.729
Yeah, that's 'cause
they're real.

17:43.731 --> 17:46.666
I got us all
two of them.

17:46.668 --> 17:48.534
Figure we could switch one out
on the road

17:48.536 --> 17:51.270
to cover our tracks.

17:51.272 --> 17:53.805
Smart.

17:53.807 --> 17:56.342
We should also find a safehouse
for after,

17:56.344 --> 17:59.545
somewhere about 15 minutes
away from the border or less,

17:59.547 --> 18:01.013
somewhere we can
hole up,

18:01.015 --> 18:02.982
just while
everything calms down.

18:04.686 --> 18:07.286
You got a plan
for after all this?

18:07.288 --> 18:08.820
Thailand.

18:08.822 --> 18:11.957
Renn and Nick just left
San Antonio, flew to Singapore.

18:11.959 --> 18:15.161
I've just been sending them
little bits of cash every day.

18:16.364 --> 18:19.098
Relax, man.
I'm not using her name.

18:19.100 --> 18:21.100
I'm gonna meet them out there,
and then, uh --

18:21.102 --> 18:24.704
yeah, then I'm
gonna fly to Phuket.

18:24.706 --> 18:26.171
How about you?

18:26.173 --> 18:28.840
Where you headed?

18:28.842 --> 18:30.442
Somewhere far
from here.

18:30.444 --> 18:33.178
I'm sick
of the beach.

18:33.180 --> 18:34.646
Yeah?

18:34.648 --> 18:35.981
Just you?

18:35.983 --> 18:38.984
What about that, uh,
chick from the law office

18:38.986 --> 18:41.320
