hanging out with?

18:41.322 --> 18:43.189
I don't know.
We'll see.

18:46.728 --> 18:49.861
♪♪

18:49.863 --> 18:51.663
Man, after living here
my whole life,

18:51.665 --> 18:53.332
it's gonna be so...

18:53.334 --> 18:55.801
weird
not seeing it again.

18:55.803 --> 18:59.205
♪♪

18:59.207 --> 19:02.074
You know, when Deran
was a little kid,

19:02.076 --> 19:03.342
