22:31.953 --> 22:33.419
He stepped up, man,
in a big way.

22:33.421 --> 22:36.822
I mean, we've been --
we've been earning.

22:36.824 --> 22:38.290
Splitting everything
evenly.

22:38.292 --> 22:40.426
I mean,
things were going great.

22:40.428 --> 22:41.693
Yeah.

22:41.695 --> 22:43.695
Then, you know...

22:43.697 --> 22:45.831
that shit happened.

22:45.833 --> 22:47.767
♪♪

22:47.769 --> 22:49.101
[ Sighs ]

22:49.103 --> 22:53.905
Deran,
you never listen to me.

22:53.907 --> 22:56.642
